# WeatherWatch Configuration

# Weather API Key (get from https://weatherapi.com)
API_KEY=your_weatherapi_key_here

# Gmail SMTP Configuration for Email Alerts
SENDER_EMAIL=your_email@gmail.com
SENDER_PASSWORD=your_gmail_app_password
RECIPIENT_EMAIL=alert_recipient@gmail.com

# NOTE: SENDER_PASSWORD must be a Gmail App Password, not your regular password
# How to get Gmail App Password:
# 1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication in Google Account
# 2. Go to Google Account → Security → App Passwords
# 3. Generate app password for "Mail"
# 4. Use the 16-character password here